280
00:12:07.160 --> 00:12:08.353
NYPD.
- Stop.

281
00:12:08.386 --> 00:12:09.996
We're about to go live.
- No. you're not.

282
00:12:10.029 --> 00:12:11.264
- Hey. hey. you can't be here.

283
00:12:11.364 --> 00:12:12.557
- Warrant says we can.
- Step aside.

284
00:12:12.624 --> 00:12:13.766
- What's going on?

285
00:12:13.833 --> 00:12:15.001
- Ann Merrick.
you're under arrest.

286
00:12:15.068 --> 00:12:16.185
- For what?

287
00:12:16.219 --> 00:12:17.704
- The murder of
Katie Harrington.

288
00:12:17.737 --> 00:12:19.038
- What the hell are
you talking about?

289
00:12:19.105 --> 00:12:20.907
Katie was my friend.
She was like my little sister.

290
00:12:27.063 --> 00:12:27.246
.

291
00:12:27.397 --> 00:12:29.816
- Earlier today. veteran
TV news anchor Ann Merrick

292
00:12:29.882 --> 00:12:31.351
was arrested on suspicion...

293
00:12:31.417 --> 00:12:33.720
- Turns out arresting
a news anchor is big news.

294
00:12:33.786 --> 00:12:35.922
- Yeah.
- How's the evidence?

295
00:12:36.022 --> 00:12:37.357
- Strong.

296
00:12:37.423 --> 00:12:39.258
Detectives found
a beanie in her apartment

297
00:12:39.325 --> 00:12:41.694
identical to the one
seen at the crime scene.

298
00:12:41.761 --> 00:12:43.921
Plus. her DNA was
on the murder weapon--

299
00:12:44.022 --> 00:12:46.224
a pair of scissors
found in her neck.

300
00:12:46.324 --> 00:12:47.867
- Motive?

301
00:12:47.934 --> 00:12:49.761
- Still not adding up.

302
00:12:49.861 --> 00:12:53.072
- So this woman suddenly
bolts from her apartment.

303
00:12:53.139 --> 00:12:55.942
